   Huang, Liangyi, Arizona State Univ, Sch Comp \& Augmented Intelligence, Tempe, AZ USA.
   Atadjanov, Ibragim R., Tashkent Univ Informat Technol Muhammad Al Khwariz, Dept Comp Engn, Tashkent 100084, Uzbekistan.},
DOI = {10.1109/JTEHM.2025.3591236},
