   hate speech and crime detection, the proposed BERT model gave great
   results with 93\% in accuracy as well as 92\% in F1 Score outperforming
   all the other models. Furthermore the results showed that states like
   Delhi, Maharashtra and Tamil Nadu have the higher chances of crime
   happening due to hate speech based on the prediction done. However the
   data may vary for different social media platforms as the current
