   Aryan, Police; Raj, Rayappa David Amar, Amrita Vishwa Vidyapeetham, Amrita Sch Artificial Intelligence, Coimbatore 641112, Tamil Nadu, India.
   Yanamala, Rama Muni Reddy, Indian Inst Informat Technol Design \& Mfg IIITDM K, Dept Elect \& Commun Engn, Chennai 600127, India.
   Pallakonda, Archana, Natl Inst Technol Warangal, Dept Comp Sci \& Engn, Warangal 506004, Telangana, India.
   Prakasha, K. Krishna, Manipal Acad Higher Educ, Manipal Inst Technol, Manipal 576104, India.},
DOI = {10.1109/ACCESS.2025.3607206},
